Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:18.55,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:24.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,A thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:29.96,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:36.68,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:41.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:48.39,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:52.56,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:57.73,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\NAs the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:06.24,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:12.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:17.25,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:23.79,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:47.20,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Macross having lost\Nits Fold System,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:51.37,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,those aboard have been forced to proceed\Nusing conventional engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:55.61,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the enemy Zentradi fleet\Nhas been tracking the Macross
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:58.04,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and hindering its progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:01.75,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Though having to fend off repeated attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.55,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,the Macross has finally passed\Nwithin the orbit of Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:18.37,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(94,145)}LONGEST BIRTHDAY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They certainly don't give up, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:28.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Their resolve is strengthening now\Nthat they're so close to their homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:32.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps we've allowed them to\Nget just a little too close...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:33.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:36.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how they'll act when they\Nrealize they're so near,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,yet they'll never be allowed to return home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:40.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they will be quite frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:42.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There is just one thing that worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin Kravshera...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:10.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Minmay's birthday, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:13.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what sort of present\Nwould make a girl happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:18.96,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention. Will the following personnel please\Nreport to the UN Forces Command Center?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.50,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Lieutenant Justy Borgnine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.50,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Lieutenant Taki Rossman...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.97,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lieutenant Yang Loo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.67,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lieutenant Marcos Myer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:29.10,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Hikaru Ichijo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:47.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, should we really be launching\Nan attack without orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a training flight, nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:52.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just happen to "accidentally"\Nencounter the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:56.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotcha. Old Man Britai will\Nbe pretty steamed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:59.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that! This time, we fight by the\Nrules of the Kamujin Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your group will be the decoys.\NDon't screw it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:05.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that. Let's give them a real show!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru Ichijo reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:25.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:27.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Y...Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like everyone's here.\NVery well, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:43.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you assembled here today\Ndistinguished yourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:45.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,during the battle on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:47.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In recognition of your valor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:51.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,we hereby award you the UN Forces\NTitanium Medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:59.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please step forward as I call your names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Lieutenant Justy Borgnine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:08.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting a medal...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:20.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.35,0:05:24.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my room for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:31.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk\Nto me about, Sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:33.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your new rank insignia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:40.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, you're a 2nd Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Put that on instead of the medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:49.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be walking around\Nshowing that thing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:50.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:55.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You get a couple of subordinates.\NThese guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:03.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayao Kakizaki, rank: Corporal.\NSimulator time: 378 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:06.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Flight time: 66 hours. Skill ranking: A.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:12.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilian Jenius, rank: Corporal.\NSimulator time: 320 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Flight time: 50 hours. Skill ranking: A.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:19.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NThey're a couple of total rookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I see it, you're not that\Nfar ahead of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can find more detailed information\Non them in the computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,along with an operations manual.\NThings a team leader needs to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:31.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote it. Study it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're here. Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:35.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:40.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is 2nd Lieutenant Hikaru Ichijo,\Nyour team leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:42.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a hero who just received\Nthe Titanium Medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo, take good care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:49.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor, sir. Damn! Uh...\NI mean, I'm Corporal Hayao Kakizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm here, you can just\Nleave everything to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:56.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I am Corporal Maximilian Jenius, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:01.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am rather inexperienced, so I would appreciate\Nany guidance you could give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure. I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:06.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:10.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai, there's somewhere I have to be, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. I'll join you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:22.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind if we join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:27.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'd be nice to show Minmay that\NI've moved up a notch or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:31.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks very much! Well then, let's be off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:36.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, just leave that to me.\NI'm taking you somewhere really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna take us to a real party, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh? Well, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:42.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}So it's somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:49.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, they're already running off\Nlike a gaggle of schoolgirls!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:56.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:59.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How could Hikaru Ichijo have been\Npromoted to team leader?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:04.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a reward for rescuing you on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:09.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A rookie like that becoming team leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the military I joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Leader! That's the "great place," right?\NThe one you were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:26.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell ya, I just love places like these!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, lookie here! This one's just opened up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've gotten the wrong idea about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's not here? Hey, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:45.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to know a lot about\Nthose sorts of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Women go wild over us soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:54.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hold on, you aren't a soldier until\Nyou actually fly a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to get into battle\Nas soon I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to end up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:22.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax! With me around, we'll do just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:25.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to get depressed about.\NJust stay close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye aye, Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Aye aye, Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I like the sound of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:36.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is it? The "great place"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:37.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru! You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:56.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you look super!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:01.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you. These\Nare my subordinates...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:03.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Corporal Kakizaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:05.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Subordinates? Hikaru, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I got promoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:12.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And this right here is Corporal Jenius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Maximilian Jenius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he's handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:20.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored to be in the presence\Nof someone so lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:24.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a flatterer, Maximilian... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:26.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just call me Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:29.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max, then. Come on, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:35.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there! Li'l Hikaru! Li'l Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:37.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:44.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:48.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I didn't forget! I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:52.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yeah, I came here straight from work,\Nand left it in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:59.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, don't be so hard\Non Li'l Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:03.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mayor, could you please stop\Ncalling me "Li'l Hikaru"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:04.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a team leader now, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Minmay, how about\Na song or somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear ya can even put pros to shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:12.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You sing, Hikaru! That can be\Nyour present to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea! C'mon, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I really can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:20.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, why don't I sing in his place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:24.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Li'l Hikaru, if you don't watch out,\Nyou're gonna lose her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:28.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'follow me, Li'l Hikaru? C'mon, get with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:31.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? There's nothing out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's strange. There's something\Nabout the radar response.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:41.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if the waves are just being\Ndispersed. Maybe it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,High-powered jamming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:01.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Almost time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:12.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Disengage jammers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:14.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Decoy group, attack at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather their bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:50.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Delicious! Really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:55.21,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention! All Valkyrie combat\Npersonnel, scramble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:58.07,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,All Valkyrie combat personnel, scramble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:06.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:08.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the bad thing about soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's a scramble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:16.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give us a ride too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:18.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No shoving!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}This isn't going to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Look, we're fine. Just get movin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Leader, that Minmay girl was really hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:27.95,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:31.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, we've just met!\NWhere is your mind at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:37.54,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I am nervous though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:41.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max, with me in this battle, it'll be like\Nhaving a thousand extra guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I wish I were that confiden... Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:20.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gunsight One! Black Squadron,\Nintercept the enemy at Block 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:21.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:23.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max, Kakizaki, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:24.54,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:24.54,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFFFFFF&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, which section are we defending?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The final line of defense for Block 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's all the way in the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, they're already seein' action over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:40.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:43.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, I'd be out there\Nwhere the fighting is, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:02.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, there's just too many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Deploy the Defenders onto the hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:18.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Defender Team 2 has been wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:20.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy formation has broken through!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:25.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,VA-102, you have enemies incoming\Nat 3 o'clock high!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.61,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here! They're here! They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:34.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kakizaki, target acquired!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakizaki, don't charge at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:43.26,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,L...Leader, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:49.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! That's why you shouldn't\Ngo rushing in by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:57.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close one. Sorry, Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier to get 'em where\Nyou want them this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:20.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like shooting fish in a barrel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:21.54,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,or whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:26.51,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:33.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking slow out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:37.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a team leader now, so get on the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:41.61,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off! It's hard to lead a team!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.61,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:55.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! They appear to have been\Nweakened in the area below the Ramidon section.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, in we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:16:59.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll embarrass the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:01.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:07.54,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakizaki, don't waste your ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:16.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all right if we DON'T waste it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.51,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Got them, Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, pursue and maintain fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:39.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we've made it this far then victory\Nis ours. Raise hell, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.12,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Close-quarter combat's my specialty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:49.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:51.93,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakizaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I made it somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard being an officer on the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You little punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:39.12,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The first one who moves, dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is typical of Kamujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:53.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange he was so\Nwilling to lead a training flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we recall him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.47,0:18:56.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:58.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,His campaign seems to be going unusually well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:01.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He has to follow the same rules as\Nthe rest of the Zentradi military.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to send a wide-area beam signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:05.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That seems rather flashy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him claiming that his\Ncomm system was damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:11.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wide-area beam signal is ready, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What message shall we send?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:15.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An order of immediate withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If they refuse, tell them they'll be sent\Nback where they came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We were so close! Damn that old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:34.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All units, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:49.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But why? I thought we were done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like perhaps they\Nhave some internal troubles of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we're saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:56.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:17.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! The body of my fighter\Nwas completely wrecked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:20.26,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What will I do if it comes out of my salary?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:22.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure did well out there, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was lucky. I shot down seven targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:27.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven?! I got zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:30.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a "genius."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:31.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:35.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no ordinary person could have\Ndone the things you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how did you fare, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Four kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That must've been my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:42.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you'd get more than Max, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:44.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:48.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm a genius, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? A genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:52.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:02.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, goodnight, Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:05.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight. Kakizaki, take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:07.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, this is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, men.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:11.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd they choose me to be team leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:21.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a lot happier taking orders\Ninstead of giving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:27.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:45.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they're closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:08.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:11.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay! I'm sorry about today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:15.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't help it.\NAfter all, you're a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.07,0:22:18.87,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And about your present...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:26.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't forget! You brought it with you,\Ndidn't you? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:35.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! This is your present.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.67,0:22:36.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:45.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:47.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can really have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.21,0:22:48.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:50.29,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.15,0:22:53.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, is somebody up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:22:56.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta go, Minmay. Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:10.40,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,For Hikaru, seeing Minmay's happy face
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:15.05,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and knowing that he was the\None who brought her joy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.19,0:23:19.25,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,means more to him than the medal\Nhe never expected to receive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:25.77,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the voyage of the Macross\Nenters its eighth month.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.46,0:23:35.37,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(58,107)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.46,0:23:35.37,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(304,441)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:40.08,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,To celebrate the launch of a ship-wide\Ntelevision network,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:43.42,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,it's decided to hold a Miss Macross contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:45.91,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay is also one of the contestants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:50.01,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, however, a Zentradi\Nrecon unit appears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:52.91,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and Hikaru flies out to intercept it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.96,0:23:55.20,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,wondering all the while about\Nthe outcome of the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:58.69,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:01.75,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(98,144)}MISS MACROSS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.69,0:24:02.45,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"MISS MACROSS"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.66,0:24:23.33,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.58,0:24:29.98,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.29,0:24:36.60,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.83,0:24:44.29,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.67,0:24:51.04,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.38,0:24:56.95,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.26,0:25:04.53,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.77,0:25:16.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
